import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useLanguage } from '../context/LanguageContext'; import './Footer.css'; const Footer = () => { const { t } = useLanguage(); const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear(); return (

{t('footerAbout')}

{t('footerAboutText')}

{t('footerWorkingHours')}

  • {t('footerWorkingDays')} {t('footerWorkingTime')}
  • {t('footerSunday')}

{t('footerContact')}

  • {t('footerAddress')}

    {t('footerAddressText')}

  • {t('footerPhone')}

    +90 (555) 123-4567

  • {t('footerEmail')}

    info@detailinx.com

{t('footerSocial')}

{t('footerFollow')}

© {currentYear} DetailinX. {t('footerRights')}

{t('footerPrivacy')} {t('footerTerms')}
); }; export default Footer;
